      "opacity": 100,
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "text": "LEGEND\n\n🟦  Client Layer\n🟧  API Gateway (AWS)\n🟩  Application (ECS Fargate)\n🟪  Domain (pure Python)\n🟥  Infrastructure\n🟨  Security\n🔵  Memory / Redis\n🟣  Workers / Celery\n── Solid arrow  = request flow\n╌╌ Dashed arrow = cross-layer call\n\nAWS Stack:\n• API Gateway → auth, throttle\n• ALB / ECS Fargate → app\n• ElastiCache Redis → sessions\n• Secrets Manager → keys\n• CloudWatch / X-Ray → observe\n\nData Flow Highlights:\n• Client → Auth → RateLimit → App\n• AuthMW → JWT/RBAC/APIKeys\n• MemSvc → Redis\n• ModelRouter → LLM Providers\n• ToolSvc → Sandboxed Tools\n• AuditSvc → Logger / DB\n• ExecuteTask -.-> Celery",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
